    :alt:   555 chip hookup

To compute R1 and C1 for a given pulse duration

1.  Enter the desired frequency.

2.  Enter any of R1 (1K-3.3M Ohms), and/or C1 (more than 0.0005 microfarads)


To reverse engineer a timer-based circuit to determine duration

1.  Enter R1 and C1

